SPOTON_APPLICATION_NAME

Set to GoldBug or Spot-On.

SPOTON_BLUETOOTH_ENABLED

Enable Bluetooth. Define if the system supports Bluetooth. Requires Qt support.

SPOTON_DATELESS_COMPILATION

If enabled, the current date-time is not included in the binary.

SPOTON_DIGITAL_SIGNATURE_HASH_ALGORITHM_STRING

Define the digital signature hash algorithm.

SPOTON_DTLS_DISABLED

DTLS is disabled if the option is provided. DTLS requires Qt support.

SPOTON_GOLDBUG

Define if preparing GoldBug.

SPOTON_GPGME_ENABLED

Enable GPGME. Requires the GPGME library.

SPOTON_LINKED_WITH_LIBGEOIP

Enable if GeoIP is desired. Requires the GeoIP library.

SPOTON_LINKED_WITH_LIBNTRU

Enable if the NTRU library is available.

SPOTON_LINKED_WITH_LIBPTHREAD

Enable if Spot-On is linked with the pthread library.

SPOTON_MACOS_OVERRIDE_NEIGHBOR_DELETE_LATER

Define in the kernel so as to override deleteLater() for the
neighbor class.

SPOTON_MCELIECE_ENABLED

Enable if McEliece is desired. Requires the NTL library.

SPOTON_POPTASTIC_SUPPORTED

Enable Poptastic.

SPOTON_POSTGRESQL_DISABLED

PostgreSQL is disabled.

SPOTON_SCTP_ENABLED

Enable SCTP. Requires system support.

SPOTON_WEBENGINE_ENABLED

Enable WebEngine. Please do not enable WebKit. Please include the
webenginewidgets module in the respective project file.

SPOTON_WEBKIT_ENABLED

Enable WebKit. Please do not enable WebEngine. Please include the
webkitwidgets module in the respective project file.

SPOTON_WEBSOCKETS_ENABLED

Enable Web sockets. Requires Qt support.
